  • Deprecated Classes 
    Classes and Description
    GxFilterDate
    since version 0.101.0, GxFilterDate is deprecated. Use GxFilterBasicDate instead.
    GxExpressionDatesFormatter
    since version 0.101.0, GxExpressionDatesFormatter is deprecated. Use GxExpressionDateTimesFormatter instead.
  • Deprecated Fields 
    Fields and Description
    GxExecutor.SuppressBuiDebouncing!
    This option is no longer used and will be removed in the future. Use `SuppressWebDebouncing` instead.
    GxColumnFilterAG.NewRowsAction!
    since version 1.7.0. This option has not replacement. The `keep` setting is now the default.
    GxFilterSetFilter.SuppressSyncValuesAfterDataChange!
    since version 1.7.0. This option has no replacement
    GxClientTransactionModel.AddIndex!
    `GxClientTransactionModel.addIndex` is deprecated. If you want precision control of adding data, use `BBjGridExWidget.updateData` instead
    GxOptionsDateTime.AllowInput!
    since version 0.101.0, GxOptionsDateTime.AllowInput is deprecated. Direct input is always disabled.
    GxDefaultColumnDefinition.PinnedRowCellRenderer!
    since v1.7.0, Setting this value won't affect the rendering. Please use the `CellRenderer` instead.
    GxOptions.SuppressSetColumnStateEvents!
    since version 1.7.0 - no longer required
    GxDefaultColumnDefinition.DefaultNumbersMask!
    - Use Mask instead
    GxDefaultColumnDefinition.DefaultStringsMask!
    - Use Mask instead
    GxDefaultColumnDefinition.DefaultDatesMask!
    - Use Mask instead
    GxDefaultColumnDefinition.DefaultTimesMask!
    - Use Mask instead
    GxDefaultColumnDefinition.DefaultTimestampsMask!
    - Use Mask instead
    GxOptions.RowDeselection!
    since v1.7.0 - use `SuppressRowDeselection` instead
    GxOptions.GroupUseEntireRow!
    since v1.7.0 - use `GroupDisplayType! = GxOptions.GROUP_DISPLAY_GROUP_ROWS() ` instead
    GxDefaultColumnGroup.HeaderGroupTooltip!
    since version 0.101.0, GxDefaultColumnGroup.HeaderGroupTooltip is deprecated / renamed. Use GxDefaultColumnGroup.HeaderToolTip instead.
    GxOptions.GroupSuppressAutoColumn!
    since v1.7.0 - use `GroupDisplayType! = GxOptions.GROUP_DISPLAY_CUSTOM()` instead
    GxOptions.GroupMultiAutoColumn!
    since v1.7.0 - use `GroupDisplayType! = GxOptions.GROUP_DISPLAY_MULTIPLE_COLUMNS()` instead
    GxOptions.GroupSuppressRow!
    since v1.7.0 - There is no replacement for this functionality.
    GxOptions.EnableFloatingFilter!
    enabling/disabling the floatingFilter on the Options level is deprecated. Use `GxColumn.FloatingFilter` on the column level instead.
    GxOptions.DeltaColumnMode!
    use `GxOptions.ImmutableColumns` instead
